---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Ways to Give" description="When you give to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, you're helping bring awareness, education, and support to individuals and families living with hoarding behavior.">

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Ways to Give</h1>

      <div class="page-banner">
        <img src="/images/ways-to-give-banner.png" alt="Heart-shaped seed pods on stems, representing growth and giving" />
      </div>

      <p class="intro-text">When you give to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, you're helping bring awareness, education, and support to individuals and families living with hoarding behavior.</p>

      <div class="give-now-section">
        <h2>Ways to Give:</h2>
        <h3 class="giving-heading">Online Donations</h3>
        <p>Online Donations are fast, easy, and convenient.</p>
        <a href="https://givebutter.com/mnhtfgeneraldonation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">GIVE NOW</a>
      </div>

      <div class="giving-details">

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Mail-In Donations</h3>
          <p>If you prefer to mail-in a donation, you can do so at the address below:<br />
            Minnesota Hoarding Task Force<br />
            P.O. Box 21483<br />
            Eagan, MN 55121</p>
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Events and Sponsors</h3>
          <p>For upcoming events and sponsorship opportunities, contact <a href="mailto:mnhtf.org@gmail.com">mnhtf.org@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Match Gifts</h3>
          <p>Help us double our impact through Corporate Giving. Check with your Employer or Human Resources Department for more information on gift matching.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">In-Kinds Gifts</h3>
          <p>By volunteering your time and talent, you help us make an impact in the community, and your contributions are invaluable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="check-image">
          <img src="/images/Handing-Over-a-Check.jpg" alt="Handing over a check" />
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Donation FAQs</h3>
          <h4 class="sub-heading">Local Donations</h4>
          <p>When you donate to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, your donation maximizes impact in bringing awareness, education, and resources to those with hoarding behavior and vulnerable individuals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Tax-Deductible</h3>
          <p>Your donation is tax-deductible, as the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force is a 501(c)(3) organization (EIN 81-3567154), which means that your donation is tax-deductible as allowed by law.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="giving-item">
          <h3 class="giving-heading">Personal Information</h3>
          <p>We respect your privacy and do not sell your email address to others. We will use it to keep you informed of MNHTF events, meetings, and information.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="contact-note">For additional information or questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:mnhtf.org@gmail.com">mnhtf.org@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="give-mn-badge">
        <a href="https://give.mn/fmb5wf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <img src="/images/HorizontalPrimary.png" alt="GiveMN — donate online" />
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ── Body text ─────────────────────────────────────── */
p {
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

/* ── Hero banner ───────────────────────────────────── */
.page-banner {
  margin: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-8);
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
}
.page-banner img {
  width: 100%;
  max-height: 280px;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center 60%;
  display: block;
}

/* ── Intro text ────────────────────────────────────── */
.intro-text {
  font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
}

/* ── "Ways to Give:" section title ─────────────────── */
h2 {
  font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 4px;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

/* ── Give Now section ──────────────────────────────── */
.give-now-section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
}
.give-now-section p {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}

/* ── Giving section headings (Mail-In, Events…) ────── */
.giving-heading {
  font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text-dark);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 4px;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
}

.sub-heading {
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text-dark);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
}

.giving-item {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
}

/* ── Check handover image ──────────────────────────── */
.check-image {
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}
.check-image img {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 680px;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
}

/* ── Contact note ──────────────────────────────────── */
.contact-note {
  margin-top: var(--space-8);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ── GiveMN badge ──────────────────────────────────── */
.give-mn-badge {
  margin: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-8);
}
.give-mn-badge img {
  width: 300px;
  height: auto;
}

/* ── Mobile ────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
  }
  .giving-heading {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }
  .page-banner img {
    max-height: 180px;
  }
}
</style>
